BOATS TO SAVE PEOPLE
────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

You are given an array people where people[i] represents the weight of the ith person.

There are infinite boats available, and each boat can carry:
• At most 2 people
• Total weight ≤ limit

Return the minimum number of boats required to carry everyone.


EXAMPLE 1
────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
Input:  people = [1,2], limit = 3
Output: 1

Explanation:
Boat 1 → (1,2)


EXAMPLE 2
────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
Input:  people = [3,2,2,1], limit = 3
Output: 3

Explanation:
Boat 1 → (1,2)  
Boat 2 → (2)  
Boat 3 → (3)


EXAMPLE 3
────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
Input:  people = [3,5,3,4], limit = 5
Output: 4

Explanation:
Boat 1 → (3)  
Boat 2 → (3)  
Boat 3 → (4)  
Boat 4 → (5)


CONSTRAINTS
────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
1 <= people.length <= 5 * 10⁴  
1 <= people[i] <= limit <= 3 * 10⁴  


APPROACH (GREEDY + TWO POINTER)
────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
1. Sort the people array
2. Use two pointers:
   • i → lightest person
   • j → heaviest person
3. Try to pair lightest with heaviest
4. If sum ≤ limit → move both pointers
5. Otherwise → heaviest goes alone
6. Each step uses one boat


TIME COMPLEXITY : O(n log n)   (sorting)  
SPACE COMPLEXITY : O(1)


CODE
────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

class Solution 
{
public:
    int numRescueBoats(vector<int>& people, int limit)
    {
        sort(people.begin(), people.end());

        int boats = 0;
        int i = 0;
        int j = people.size() - 1;

        while(i <= j)
        {
            if(people[i] + people[j] <= limit)
            {
                i++;
            }

            j--;
            boats++;
        }

        return boats;
    }
};
